;       TAPEMEASURE::GETPROPERTY
;
; PURPOSE:
;
;       This method allows the user to obtain TAPEMEASURE properties. Be sure
;       you ALWAYS call the superclass GETPROPERTY method if you have extra
;       keywords!
;
; SYNTAX:
;
;       theObject -> GetProperty ...
;
; ARGUMENTS:
;
